entries.femaleVariant: A gig well done, V. Our client's satisfied not only to get his hands on that recording, but the wheels too.
The gig's done. Good. But you had a chance to get those wheels back and you didn't. Shame.
A satisfied client means a generous client, and a generous client means a generous fixer. Try to remember that. Contract closed.
A satisfied client means a satisfied fixer. Hell, you should be satisfied too. Contract's closed and payment's on its way.
